```r
summary(lmer(data = sinspuAlpha,
             Shannon ~ virus.bin +(1|patientid)))

sinspuAlpha %>%
  group_by(virus.bin,sampleloc) %>%
  identify_outliers(Shannon) %>%
  .$index -> Shannonoutliers

sinspuAlpha %>%
  group_by(virus.bin,sampleloc) %>%
  identify_outliers(Simpson) %>%
  .$index -> Simpsonoutliers

sinspuAlpha %>%
  mutate(outlier = if_else(index %in% Shannonoutliers,TRUE,FALSE)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = virus.bin,
             y = Shannon,
             color = sampleloc)) +
  #geom_boxplot(outliers = FALSE) +
  geom_violin(draw_quantiles = c(0.5),
              trim = TRUE) +
  geom_jitter(aes(shape = outlier),
              width = 0.1,
              size = 5,
              alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_color_manual(values = loccols,
                     guide = \none\") +
